Introduction

Dongmyeong is a member of the band ONEWE under RBW Entertainment. He is the vocalist and keyboardist of the group.

He represented RBW on Produce 101 Season 2 but was eliminated in the 5th episode, securing the 68th position.

On October 2017, Dongmyeong and M.A.S participated for 'The Unit'. Although he reached the finale, he was eliminated in 16th place.
